'''diode'''

# An [[electronic]] [[device]] that [[allow]]s [[current]] to [[flow]] in one [[direction]] only; a [[valve]].
# A two-terminal [[semiconductor]] device, having a [[p-n junction]], used chiefly as a [[rectifier]].

